      <title>特朗普说，勒庞定罪是“大事”，与他的案件类似</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-le-pen-conviction-is-big-deal-similar-to-his-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）因挪用公款被定罪，并将其法律困境比作他在夺回权力之前所面临的起诉后，为极右翼法国领导人马林·勒庞（Marine Le Pen）提供了支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-le-pen-conviction-is-big-deal-similar-to-his-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:26:33 GMT</pubDate>
